What does the abbreviation "RMPV" on a HP datasheet stand for?
A. Recommended Monthly Page Volume
B. Robust Middle Paper Ventilation
C. Regular Maximum Paper Volume
D. Reverse Motor Power Value
Answer: A
Reference:http://acronyms.thefreedictionary.com/Recommended+Monthly+Page+Volume
